43
00:03:39,843 --> 00:03:43,289
<i>Covek- zvuci dostojanstveno.</i>

44
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:07,111
Dežurni oficir

45
00:04:27,181 --> 00:04:28,434
Korak nazad.

46
00:04:41,395 --> 00:04:45,019
Mirno.
Napred marš.

47
00:05:06,082 --> 00:05:07,184
