ispred nas - Bugarska,

786
01:25:20,807 --> 01:25:23,304
Iza nas - Dunav.

787
01:25:24,326 --> 01:25:27,355
Puno smo prešli,

788
01:25:28,273 --> 01:25:30,703
preko vode i kopna,

789
01:25:31,268 --> 01:25:34,391
ali našu Sovjetsku otadžbinu

790
01:25:35,008 --> 01:25:36,656
nismo zaboravili.

791
01:25:46,400 --> 01:25:49,756
I pod zvezdama Balkana

792
01:25:49,840 --> 01:25:51,620
uporno se secamo,

793
01:25:52,394 --> 01:25:55,326
Jaroslav, Rezanski,

794
01:25:55,961 --> 01:25:57,797
i Smolenski sela.

795
01:26:07,560 --> 01:26:10,950
Secamo se braon ociju,

796
01:26:11,040 --> 01:26:12,845
tihog glasa, zvonkog smeha.

797
01:26:13,433 --> 01:26:19,635
Bugarska je lepa zemlja
ali Rusija je najbolja."

